==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|jûrm}}, {{IPA|/dʒɜː(r)m/}}, {{SAMPA|/dZ3:(r)m/}}
*:'''Rhymes''': [[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)m|-ɜː(r)m]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{biology}} The small [[mass]] of [[cell]]s from which a new [[organism]] [[develop]]s; a [[seed]], [[bud]] or [[spore]].
# A [[pathogenic]] [[microorganism]].
# An [[idea]] that forms the [[basis]] of some [[project]].
# The [[embryo]] of a [[seed]], especially of a seed used as a [[cereal]] or [[grain]].  See [[w:Cereal germ|Wikipedia article on cereal germ]].

